{"tid":1157404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾有人預言 香港將於2019年5月23日發生地震？","createTime":"2019-05-16T08:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T03:58:13.000Z","uid":252289,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d0bca4c23e3051623aceb69cdcca3c0131455b56","tid":1157404,"uid":252289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jq0kghy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJq0kghy.jpg&h=a111adc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（講明先：唔係想宣傳個專頁）<br />\n尋晚大約凌晨三四點瞓瞓下feel到個地面搖動，之後今日咪搵下有無新聞講地震；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知睇到有個fb page講香港地震，最頂個帖子仲要係有人2014年5月23日預言<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五年後香港會發生大地震</span>。<br />\n<br />\n雖然2012預言有話會世界末日最後無發生到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但今次個預言大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假㗎啲奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e465b25c650fd8c087f1ba330db3b92813bda0f","tid":1157404,"uid":35192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ONYe0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FONYe0.png&h=4957ee15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cf1b293bc76f03d6566b92540c919216c90c490","tid":1157404,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:04:05.000Z","msg":"巴西預言家"},{"pid":"d7c673ee5449bfc8c0e48d64a07f9eef573548d8","tid":1157404,"uid":2752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"巴西預言家預言 2019年5月23日9點 香港出現黎克特製7級大地震<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1029341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1029341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c96a94cbf52b1b7e414599bcdc4d048fc3abfe92","tid":1157404,"uid":26053,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-